01:13:45.500 --> 01:13:49.125
Everybody needs somebody.

01:13:49.166 --> 01:13:52.750
Stop trying to act likeyou're different.

01:13:56.250 --> 01:13:57.000
Alex, where have you been?

01:13:57.041 --> 01:13:58.583
