We can go up anytime.

01:14:18.875 --> 01:14:20.541
Do you want us to go inwith you?

01:14:20.583 --> 01:14:24.041
Well, if you don't mindI'd like to go in alone.

01:14:24.083 --> 01:14:26.000
Of course,we'll wait here.

01:14:26.041 --> 01:14:28.416
Take as long as you want,okay?

01:14:33.125 --> 01:14:36.166
(P.A.) Dr. Reynolds, you have a call at Nurse's station 2.

01:14:36.208 --> 01:14:40.375
Dr. Reynolds, you have a call at Nurse's station 2.

01:15:10.875 --> 01:15:12.541
Mom?

01:15:26.375 --> 01:15:29.375
Sorry I never cameto see you.

01:15:58.625 --> 01:16:01.333
I wrote to you.

01:16:01.375 --> 01:16:03.041
I don't know whyI didn't send them

01:16:03.125 --> 01:16:05.958
but I want you to havethem now.

01:16:22.916 --> 01:16:25.875
I'm sorry abouteverything mom.

01:16:35.708 --> 01:16:37.041
Alex.

01:16:42.875 --> 01:16:44.375
Should we go talk to him?

01:16:44.375 --> 01:16:45.083
Not right now.

01:16:45.125 --> 01:16:45.875
He needs a little timeto deal

01:16:45.958 --> 01:16:47.333
with whateverhappened back there.

01:16:47.375 --> 01:16:51.916
His Harvard interviewis tomorrow.

01:16:51.958 --> 01:16:53.916
Come on.

01:16:56.375 --> 01:16:57.625
[knocking]

01:16:57.708 --> 01:16:59.083
Come in.

01:17:03.250 --> 01:17:04.958
I brought you somehot chocolate,

01:17:05.000 --> 01:17:06.458
put little marshmallowsin it.

01:17:06.500 --> 01:17:08.208
Jen likes it that way.

01:17:08.250 --> 01:17:10.708
I thought maybeyou would too.

01:17:10.750 --> 01:17:12.875
Thanks.

01:17:12.916 --> 01:17:16.041
Here you go.

01:17:16.083 --> 01:17:17.583
Anything else you need, Alex?

01:17:17.625 --> 01:17:18.958
Anything at all?

01:17:19.041 --> 01:17:20.833
No.

01:17:22.291 --> 01:17:23.916
Okay.

01:17:25.875 --> 01:17:29.083
I'm sorry Mrs. Bante.

01:17:29.166 --> 01:17:30.833
Sorry for what?

01:17:30.875 --> 01:17:34.000
You tried to do allthis nice stuff for me

01:17:34.041 --> 01:17:35.875
and I couldn't handle it.

01:17:35.875 --> 01:17:40.208
I wasn't used to it.

01:17:40.250 --> 01:17:41.875
I know.

01:17:41.916 --> 01:17:44.500
You thought I was tryingto take your mother's place.

01:17:44.541 --> 01:17:48.375
You do all the thingsthat I needed her to do.

01:17:48.416 --> 01:17:50.708
I feel guilty thinking thatyou were better at it

01:17:50.708 --> 01:17:51.708
than she was.

01:17:51.750 --> 01:17:55.041
Alex, your mother couldn'tgive you what you needed

01:17:55.083 --> 01:18:00.583
but I know she triedas hard as she could.

01:18:00.625 --> 01:18:02.125
How can you be so sure?

01:18:02.208 --> 01:18:06.000
Because I know how mucha mother loves a child,

01:18:06.041 --> 01:18:08.541
how much we wantto protect them.

01:18:08.583 --> 01:18:09.708
And if we're unableto do that

01:18:09.791 --> 01:18:13.708
it's because it's outof our control.

01:18:13.750 --> 01:18:17.458
It's the worst feelingin the world.

01:18:17.500 --> 01:18:22.666
I know your mother lovesyou Alex, I know it.

01:18:22.708 --> 01:18:25.000
And so do I.

01:18:32.875 --> 01:18:34.291
[knocks]

01:18:34.333 --> 01:18:36.250
Rise and shine buddy,today's the big day.

01:18:36.291 --> 01:18:38.291
Suzanne pressed your suit,picked out a tie,

01:18:38.333 --> 01:18:41.208
and we're having French toastfor breakfast.

01:19:08.041 --> 01:19:10.333
Alex, why aren't you dressed?

01:19:10.375 --> 01:19:11.541
Yeah, your interviewis at 11:00.

01:19:11.583 --> 01:19:13.708
It's all the wayacross town.

01:19:13.750 --> 01:19:15.541
I'm not going.

01:19:15.541 --> 01:19:17.708
What?

01:19:17.791 --> 01:19:20.041
I mean, what's the point?

01:19:20.083 --> 01:19:23.833
I've just been kidding myself.

01:19:23.875 --> 01:19:26.250
Why would Harvardtake a kid like me?

01:19:26.291 --> 01:19:28.041
I've been in and outof seven foster homes

01:19:28.125 --> 01:19:29.333
and nothing ever works out

01:19:29.375 --> 01:19:32.083
so why would this beany different?

01:19:32.125 --> 01:19:34.000
I'll tell you why, Alex,

01:19:34.041 --> 01:19:35.916
because you have a gift.

01:19:35.958 --> 01:19:38.166
One that you inheritedfrom your mom,

01:19:38.208 --> 01:19:40.291
and her of all peoplewould hate to see you

01:19:40.333 --> 01:19:42.208
throw that gift away.

01:19:42.250 --> 01:19:45.500
Did something happenat the hospital?

01:19:45.541 --> 01:19:49.708
If you talk about itmaybe we can help.

01:19:49.708 --> 01:19:51.375
Please.

01:19:53.875 --> 01:19:57.916
When I was 10 and I sawher in the hospitaltfor the first time,

01:19:58.000 --> 01:19:59.875
you know what really gotto me?

01:19:59.875 --> 01:20:01.791
It was her hands.

01:20:01.833 --> 01:20:04.125
At the time I calledthem her alligator hand

01:20:04.166 --> 01:20:06.541
because she had themcurled up tight

01:20:06.583 --> 01:20:10.875
against her chestlike this.

01:20:10.958 --> 01:20:15.250
I saw those same hands againlast night.

01:20:15.291 --> 01:20:19.458
After all these yearsnothing's changed.

01:20:19.500 --> 01:20:20.541
She's never goingto get better

01:20:20.583 --> 01:20:22.375
and it's always goingto be the same.

01:20:22.416 --> 01:20:24.500
You can't give into that.

01:20:26.875 --> 01:20:28.291
But what if I end uplike my mother?

01:20:28.333 --> 01:20:31.208
Alex, that is not goingto happen.

01:20:31.250 --> 01:20:33.208
I just wanted her to tell meI could do it.

01:20:33.250 --> 01:20:36.041
She knows you can do it.

01:20:36.083 --> 01:20:38.916
And so do we.

01:20:39.000 --> 01:20:40.666
You know what, Alex,

01:20:40.708 --> 01:20:45.708
we haven't asked a lot of youbut we're asking now.

01:20:45.708 --> 01:20:48.333
Go upstairs,put that suit on

01:20:48.375 --> 01:20:51.541
and let's get youto that interview.

01:21:04.541 --> 01:21:07.875
Firm handshake, right?

01:21:07.875 --> 01:21:10.833
That's right.

01:21:26.916 --> 01:21:28.916
Alex Chivescu?

01:21:29.000 --> 01:21:30.833
How do you do?

01:21:30.875 --> 01:21:34.875
Please come on up,we've got lots to talk about.

01:22:21.375 --> 01:22:22.541
Well, how'd it go?

01:22:22.583 --> 01:22:24.500
I gave it my best shot.

01:22:24.541 --> 01:22:25.833
That's my boy.

01:22:25.875 --> 01:22:27.916
Come on.

01:22:37.416 --> 01:22:39.416
Jim, it's here!

01:22:41.875 --> 01:22:42.708
It's here?

01:22:42.708 --> 01:22:45.583
Yeah.

01:22:45.625 --> 01:22:47.666
It's hereNow before I open this,

01:22:47.708 --> 01:22:49.791
there's a couple thingsI want to say.

01:22:49.875 --> 01:22:50.875
Okay.

01:22:50.916 --> 01:22:55.041
First, I respect you bothMr. and Mrs. Bante,

01:22:55.083 --> 01:22:58.083
more than anyone elseI've ever known.

01:22:58.166 --> 01:23:04.041
Second, I used to thinkthat this was everything.

01:23:04.041 --> 01:23:06.750
Now I still hope I get in

01:23:06.750 --> 01:23:08.791
but if I don't I'll gosomewhere else

01:23:08.875 --> 01:23:13.541
because the thing is I alreadyhave what matters most,I get in

01:23:16.083 --> 01:23:17.458
a family.

01:23:24.500 --> 01:23:27.000
Alex, open it.

01:23:27.041 --> 01:23:28.375
[laughs]

01:23:49.250 --> 01:23:50.291
I made it.

01:23:50.375 --> 01:23:52.583
What?

01:23:52.666 --> 01:23:53.833
I made it!!!!!!!

01:23:53.875 --> 01:23:55.666
[laughing]Yeah!!!!!!

01:23:55.708 --> 01:23:57.375
He's going to Harvard!

01:23:57.416 --> 01:23:59.666
I gotta call Jen and Lucyand Danny!

01:23:59.708 --> 01:24:01.208
Go, go, go!

01:24:01.208 --> 01:24:02.458
He did it, Jim!

01:24:02.541 --> 01:24:03.708
No, we did it.

01:24:03.750 --> 01:24:05.166
[laughter]

01:24:05.208 --> 01:24:06.166
That's good, right I got this.

01:24:06.208 --> 01:24:08.000
Okay squeeze in you guys, squeeze in.

01:24:08.041 --> 01:24:10.708
Alright Eagle Creek gradssay 2009.

01:24:10.708 --> 01:24:13.000
(All): 2009!

01:24:13.041 --> 01:24:14.875
That's good that's good,one more,

01:24:14.916 --> 01:24:16.458
one more, 2009.

01:24:16.541 --> 01:24:18.541
(All): 2009!

01:24:27.708 --> 01:24:29.375
Oh man!

01:24:29.416 --> 01:24:33.208
[applause]

01:24:33.208 --> 01:24:34.083
I don't believe it,

01:24:34.166 --> 01:24:35.750
I'll be right back.

01:24:38.166 --> 01:24:39.875
I can't believe youguys came!

01:24:39.875 --> 01:24:41.708
My man, of coursewe came!

01:24:41.791 --> 01:24:43.958
We couldn't missthis party!

01:24:45.208 --> 01:24:47.541
Listen, you need any helpwith that college algebra

01:24:47.583 --> 01:24:48.708
you know who to call.

