Yeah, how've you been,Carlos?

01:24:50.083 --> 01:24:50.916
I'm good.

01:24:50.916 --> 01:24:52.958
I'm working, goingto community college

01:24:53.000 --> 01:24:53.583
Yeah?I'm good.

01:24:53.666 --> 01:24:54.875
Taking classes in welding.

01:24:54.958 --> 01:24:57.208
You 'otta see this guywith a blowtorch.

01:24:57.250 --> 01:24:58.125
I'm awesome.

01:24:58.208 --> 01:25:00.166
Yeah, I bet you are.

01:25:03.125 --> 01:25:06.708
Um, excuse me.

01:25:15.541 --> 01:25:18.541
I am so proud of you.

01:25:18.583 --> 01:25:20.375
Thank you.

01:25:20.458 --> 01:25:22.500
Thanks for coming, mom.

01:25:22.541 --> 01:25:25.875
I wouldn't missthis for the world.

01:25:28.041 --> 01:25:29.833
I read your letters,

01:25:29.875 --> 01:25:33.625
It really means a lot to methat you wrote them.

01:25:33.666 --> 01:25:35.541
I'm sorry I nevermailed them.

01:25:35.625 --> 01:25:38.083
No, Alex I'm sorry.

01:25:38.083 --> 01:25:41.208
I'm so very sorryyou had to go through

01:25:41.291 --> 01:25:44.250
Noeverything you went through.

01:25:44.333 --> 01:25:47.416
It wasn't your fault, mom.

01:25:47.500 --> 01:25:50.041
Thanks for that.

01:25:50.083 --> 01:25:56.375
Anyway, I got you something.

01:25:56.458 --> 01:26:00.208
